      (A) Name, address, and telephone number of the solid waste management division;


      (B) Name and address of the site owner and/or operator;


      (C) Location and size of the proposed site;


      (D) Brief description of the type of operation to be operated at the site and the type of waste that will be accepted;


      (E) A description of the time frame and procedures for making a final determination on the facility application approval or disapproval;  and


